== Internet Relay Chat ==
* freenode.net
** #forth - general discussion (FnFC)
** ##forth - general discussion (alternate channel)
** #forth-ev - discussion in German on Wednesdays, starting 8:15 PM GMT+1
** #c4th colorForth discussion (basically dead)
** #retro - RetroForth discussion

FIG-UK used to hold monthly meetings on IRCNet, but this seems to have died out.  Jenny Brien apparently tried to revive them on freenode (see [http://tunes.org/~nef/logs/forth/06.10.19 this log]) but it didn't happen.

